<b>Michael Paul Koplove</b> (born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../794/1794.xml">
August 30</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../661/34661.xml">
1976</link> in <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../585/50585.xml">
