 he was 4-2 with 14 saves and a 2.50 ERA in 51 relief appearances.<weblink xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="http://web.minorleaguebaseball.com/milb/stats/stats.jsp?n=Mike%2520Koplove&amp;pos=P&amp;sid=t422&amp;t=p_pbp&amp;pid=407377">
http://web.minorleaguebaseball.com/milb/stats/stats.jsp?n=Mike%2520Koplove&amp;pos=P&amp;sid=t422&amp;t=p_pbp&amp;pid=407377</weblink> In <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../405/13639405.xml">
2008</link>, with the <diversion wordnetid="100426928" confidence="0.8">
<event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
<baseball_team wordnetid="108079319" confidence="0.8">
