<sec>
<st>
Major leagues</st>

<ss1>
<st>
Arizona Diamondbacks</st>
<p>

He played for the Diamondbacks <series wordnetid="108457976" confidence="0.8">
<operation wordnetid="100955060" confidence="0.8">
<arrangement wordnetid="107938773" confidence="0.8">
<event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
